{"tid":1168572,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界最麻煩昆蟲沒有之一","createTime":"2019-05-23T18:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:34:23.000Z","uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0b0f772cad9a8886dbc82b1ea8cd548bef9de74f","tid":1168572,"uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:28:28.000Z","msg":"係蚤呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟早前屋企裝修，於是連埋隻貓一齊出去短租<br />\n租嗰間屋有煙霧探測，問咗業主 佢話唔可以用滅蟲嘅煙彈<br />\n諗住用消毒藥水清潔好就無事<br />\n<br />\n點知<br />\n<br />\n只係短短一星期，已經係貓貓身上發現有蚤<br />\n幫貓加強清潔除蟲梳毛之後，啲蚤就開始咬人<br />\n咬我都唔緊要，我仲坦得住<br />\n但每次見到隻貓成身蚤屎都覺得好苦惱<br />\n<br />\n屋企一搞掂就馬上搬返去啦<br />\n今次做好哂滅蚤滅蟲，又帶咗隻貓去寵物店煎熬兩小時（沖涼）<br />\n幸福咗一星期，啲蚤 又 返 嚟 啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經日日幫隻貓梳毛，每月漏蚤水，防蚤頸帶又試過，屋企吸塵，消毒藥水抹地同抹貓經常逗留嘅地方，保持屋企乾爽（開冷氣），連窗都唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解仲係有蚤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94caf3730a056da26985532e1af470cef6201e4","tid":1168572,"uid":123329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"搵d封箱膠紙又好咩都好 塞死個煙霧頭再放蚤彈博個煙霧頭唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8800e4ae442597d4c56cb2e94b13807c80ac2e89","tid":1168572,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94caf3730a056da26985532e1af470cef6201e4","tid":1168572,"uid":123329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"搵d封箱膠紙又好咩都好 塞死個煙霧頭再放蚤彈博個煙霧頭唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係已經搬咗返自己屋企啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db382aa6c719ece9963e45e58664642dd9617acf","tid":1168572,"uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94caf3730a056da26985532e1af470cef6201e4","tid":1168572,"uid":123329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"搵d封箱膠紙又好咩都好 塞死個煙霧頭再放蚤彈博個煙霧頭唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:33:54.000Z","msg":"嗰下又醒唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早知唔理直接焗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6962b90a140e95654590a304302bfc5bff540d9e","tid":1168572,"uid":27596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8800e4ae442597d4c56cb2e94b13807c80ac2e89","tid":1168572,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f94caf3730a056da26985532e1af470cef6201e4","tid":1168572,"uid":123329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"搵d封箱膠紙又好咩都好 塞死個煙霧頭再放蚤彈博個煙霧頭唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T18:55:15.000Z","msg":"樓主唔係已經搬咗返自己屋企啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:34:23.000Z","msg":"返咗仲慘<br />\n已經帶哂啲蚤返屋企"}]}